OL,6,FThe NUJ claims BBC management
OL,7,Frejected proposals to trial a one-
OL,8,Fhour breakfast programme. The union
OL,9,Fsays it believes 10 staff at the
OL,10,FDerry station remain at risk of
OL,11,Fredundancy.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
