PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1679953194
OL,6,F"The announcement of a new schedule,
OL,7,Fdue to come into effect on April 24,
OL,8,Fis deeply disappointing and leaves
OL,9,Fthe NUJ with no option but to put
OL,10,Fthis matter into dispute."As a result
OL,11,Fof the strong stand taken by the NUJ
OL,12,Fand the massive public support for
OL,13,FBBC Radio Foyle across the North West
OL,14,Fregion, we have succeeded in securing
OL,15,Fhourly radio bulletins and retaining
OL,16,Fthe principle of a breakfast news
OL,17,Fprogramme on the station. The NUJ had
OL,18,Fproposed a 1-hour Breakfast Show for
OL,19,Fa trial period but management has dug
OL,20,Fin on the idea of a 30-minute
OL,21,Fprogramme.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
