PN,35405
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1679953194
OL,6,F"Having entered into this process in
OL,7,Fgood faith we were very disappointed
OL,8,Fwith the hard-line position taken by
OL,9,Fmanagement. We have now written to
OL,10,Fmanagement and informed them that we
OL,11,Fdispute the matter and will have to
OL,12,Fmove forward with a ballot for
OL,13,Findustrial action. There is still
OL,14,Ftime for management to reconsider its
OL,15,Fposition. The NUJ, public
OL,16,Frepresentatives and community groups
OL,17,Fmade a strong and coherent case for
OL,18,Fthe retention of the Breakfast Show.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,E]GArticle Published -- 29-Apr-22 2345
FL,355,353,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
PN,35406
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1679953194
OL,6,F"The public reaction, reflected in
OL,7,Fpetitions, meetings, rallies and
OL,8,Fparliamentary interventions, is a
OL,9,Fmeasure of the importance of BBC
OL,10,FRadio Foyle. The retention of
OL,11,Fregional bulletins and the principle
OL,12,Fthat there should be a Breakfast Show
OL,13,Ffrom the Foyle studio are significant
OL,14,Fachievements.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
