FL,355,353,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
PN,35407
SC,0007
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1679953194
OL,6,F"Having reached a measure of
OL,7,Fconsensus it is entirely unreasonable
OL,8,Fto pull the plug and to announce a
OL,9,Fnew, diminished schedule with a
OL,10,Ffanfare which will not succeed in
OL,11,Fconvincing anyone that this is in the
OL,12,Fbest interest of BBC Radio Foyle or
OL,13,Fstaff.
OL,15,F"We will continue to campaign for a
OL,16,Fstronger commitment to Radio Foyle by
OL,17,Fthe BBC and are confident that we
OL,18,Fhave the support of the people who
OL,19,Fmatter most ` the daily listeners
OL,20,Facross the North West."
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
