OL,6,FIn a statement, BBC Northern Ireland
OL,7,Finterim director Adam Smyth said the
OL,8,Fchanges "reflect our commitment to
OL,9,FFoyle as a production centre for
OL,10,Flocal and region-wide output".
OL,12,F"News will remain a core part of its
OL,13,Fwork, focussing on stories and issues
OL,14,Faffecting BBC audiences across the
OL,15,Fwhole of the north west," he added.
